      "name": "Personal pronouns in the nominative",
      "explanation": "Use я (I), ты (you, singular informal), вы (you, singular formal or plural), он (he), она (she), оно (it), мы (we), and они (they). The form вы covers both politeness toward one stranger and address to a group.",
