      "level": "A1",
      "name": "Possessive pronouns",
      "explanation": "Distinguish agreeing possessives мой/твой/наш/ваш (they change form: моя книга, моё окно) from the invariable forms его/её/их. The agreeing set must agree with the gender and number of the possessed noun, not the possessor.",
